ce:section.ce:para:
Hela cells were initially treated with Graphenin and the total RNA was then extracted using MiniBEST Universal RNA Extraction Kit (Takara, Japan). A PrimeScript RT Reagent Kit was utilized to synthesize Cdna from the total RNA (1 μg). Real-time quantitative PCR was performed using a CFX96 Real-Time PCR Detection System (Bio-Rad, USA). The levels of total RNA were normalized to GAPDH. The 2−ΔΔCt method was utilized to normalize the expression of the indicated genes. The sequences of the primers are listed as following:


Casp3 forward 5′-AGAACTGGACTGTGGCATTGAG-3′;



Casp3 reverse 5′-GCTTGTCGGCATACTGTTTCAG-3′;



Casp8 forward 5′-CTCCCCAAACTTGCTTTATG-3′;



Casp8 reverse 5′-AAGACCCCAGAGCATTGTTA-3′;



Bcl-2 forward 5′-GGTGGGGTCATGTGTGTGG-3′;



Bcl-2 reverse 5′-CGGTTCAGGTACTCAGTCATCC-3′;



Bax forward 5′-CATGTTTTCTGACGGCCAACTTC-3′;



Bax reverse 5′-AGGGCCTTGAGCACCAGTTT-3′;



p53 forward 5′-TCAACAAGATGTTTTGCCAACTG-3′;



p53 reverse 5′-ATGTGCTGTGACTGCTTGTAGATG-3′;



GAPDH forward 5′-GATTCCACCCATGGCAAATTC-3′;



GAPDH reverse 5′- AGCATCGCCCCACTTGATT-3′.
